    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_306714866290573967.png",
                "id": "talent59345",
                "key": "断雨",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "断雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>切换<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">近战状态</span>，然后造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，并使目标角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">断流</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/04e544f76342ce9857c812b10e4d0f87_7541771971182739642.png",
                "id": "talent94888",
                "key": "魔王武装·狂澜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔王武装·狂澜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>依据<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">达达利亚</span>当前所处的状态，进行不同的攻击：</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">远程状态</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> · </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">魔弹一闪：</span>造成5点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，返还2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span>，目标角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">断流</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">近战状态</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> · </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">尽灭水光：</span>造成7点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/b302ce0c0075ea711befbddc08555b75_6429611164199383552.png",
                "id": "talent96388",
                "key": "极恶技 · 尽灭闪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "极恶技 · 尽灭闪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">远程状态</span>。</p><p>角色所附属的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">近战状态</span>效果结束后，重新附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">远程状态</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/3e90a55bd72193eae8ddd2475b84577d_3471124927688288227.png",
                "id": "talent91294",
                "key": "遏浪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "遏浪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_886213828164458492.png",
                "id": "talent52764",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">近战状态</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>转换为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色进行重击后：</span>目标角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">断流</span>。</p><p>角色对附属有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">断流</span>的角色造成的伤害+1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色对已附属有断流的角色使用技能后：</span>对下一个敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。（每回合至多2次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">重击</span></strong></p><p>我方开始行动前，如果元素骰总数为偶数，则进行的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「普通攻击」</span>将被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「重击」</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">断流</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色被击倒后：</span>对所在阵营的出战角色附属「断流」。</p><p>（处于<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「近战状态」</span>的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">达达利亚</span>攻击所附属角色时，会造成额外伤害。）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">充能</span></strong></p><p>角色使用「元素爆发」时，需要消耗充能。</p><p>角色使用「元素战技」或「普通攻击」后，会获得1点充能。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">远程状态</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色进行重击后：</span>目标角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">断流</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5614955607300840890.png",
